<plot>Memorial documentary tribute to actor 'Desmond Llewelyn' (qv) who appeared in seventeen Eon Productions James Bond movies. The short features on the _World Is Not Enough, The (1999)_ (qv) DVD - both Special and Ultimate Editions as this was the last Bond movie that he worked on. Tribute is a compilation of clips from his films played to one of the most famous James Bond title songs, "Nobody Does It Better" by 'Carly Simon' (qv), and includes a prologue and an epigraph.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?617877</url></doc>
